data.description: This recently updated Cape Coral POOL home features three spacious bedrooms, two bathrooms, separate living & family room. Split floor concept boasts an inviting kitchen/living room area that is great for entertaining while overlooking your tranquil pool views. This home also sports a newer roof, HVAC, roof/facia, recently remodeled master bath, recently-redone plumbing, updated kitchen, & newer Samsung appliances! ALL  ASSESSMENTS IN AND PAID!  Within walking distance of the beautiful riverfront Horton Park and boat ramp! Be out to the river in mere minutes! Large, fenced-in yard a perfect spot for children/play, or to store your boat! This neighborhood is very sought-after, and homes in this price range don't often come on the market! Centrally located with lightning-fast access to shopping, dinning, entertainment & all other daily needs! The sellers have lovingly taken care of this home & the value will be passed onto the next lucky owner. Schedule your showing today!
